title: Kendall Jenner flaunts pink locks in Vogue Spread
text: Kendall Jenner flaunts pink locks in Vogue Spread Wednesday, 21 October 2015 (4 minutes ago) , Oct. 21(ANI): Kendall Jenner is one of those who experiment quite often and this time she has given her hair some pinky twist. Kendall Jenner Rocks Pink Hair for Vogue 00:41 Kendall Jenner rocked some rosy locks for her latest Vogue spread, which also featured her famous friends Gigi Hadid, Jaden Smith, and Nick Jonas. The spread is to show the new class of CFDA/Vogue Fashion Fund finalists, and the emerging designers were posed next to these stars, with Jenner standing...
